UNIVERSAL VISION said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 1.90% to NT$58,662,000 from NT$57,571,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales             58,662           57,571    
YOY%              1.90%    -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            322,866          335,821    
YOY%              -3.86% 
=================================================================
 